
How to run the program

It is required that the system is installed with JDK 1.8 and git.

Step 1: Clone the project
	git clone https://github.com/dliuvt/work-sample.git

Step 2: move to the work-sample folder
	cd ./work-sample

Step 3: check if java classes are cloned

	ls -l ./edu/vt/


Step 4: compile the java clases

	javac -cp . ./edu/vt/SortText.java


Step 5: Run the java class and enter the text to be sorted

	java -cp . edu.vt.SortText


